*Basic command for windows networks*

    ipconfig - configuration of network

Parameters:

      /all - full configuration

      /renew - ruquest new ipv4 from DHCP

      /release - realeses the current ipv4 from DHCP

      /displaydns & / flushdns - for diagnostic DNS

      /registerdns - re-gisters DNS name of PC in DNS

      /renew & /release - for ipv6
